Steps : 
Shutdown vCenter Server
Take a snapshot 
Turn On vCenter and ensure all services are running
Check root/administrator passwords are working
Download vCenter 7.0 U2 (ISO location : HX Veeam)
Check last vCenter backup is completed
Perform Upgrade
Increase vCPU and RAM
Convert license and install
Check vCener backups in new instance.
